text:
The #UAE has administered 10,194,276 doses of the #Covid19Vaccine to date, authorities announced.

Official data released on Saturday, April 24, said 87,592 doses of the vaccine were administered in the last 24 hours. The net dose rate is 103.07 per 100 people.
